             was indicted for <rs id="t17970712-56-off309" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970712-56-off309" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970712-56-off309" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               forging and counterfeiting, on the <rs id="t17970712-56-cd310" type="crimeDate">27th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-56-off309 t17970712-56-cd310"></join>, a certain order for payment of money, purporting to be the order of 
                     <persName id="t17970712-56-person592">
                        William
                         Cavendish
                     <interp inst="t17970712-56-person592" type="surname" value="Cavendish"></interp>
