                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-56-victim598 t17970712-56-viclabel311"></join>, London, dated Yarmouth, 1st May, 1797. for the payment of five guineas to George Wilkinson, Esq. or bearer, for value received, with intention to defraud 
                     <persName id="t17970712-56-victim593" type="victimName">
                        John
                        <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179707120045"></xptr>
                        Pybus
                     <interp inst="t17970712-56-victim593" type="surname" value="Pybus"></interp>
